{"id": "art-1533", "label": "Art. 1533", "title": "Art. 1533", "slug": "art-1533", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1257267788\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2131\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1257267788\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>3</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2143029292\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2130\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2143029292\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Directoratul reprezint&#259; societatea în raport cu <span\nclass=SpellE>ter&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în <span\nclass=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_210951050\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2129\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_210951050\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În lipsa unei <span class=SpellE>stipula&#355;ii</span>\ncontrare în actul constitutiv, membrii directoratului reprezint&#259;\nsocietatea doar <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> împreun&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_319430858\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2128\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_319430858\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> în care\nmembrii directoratului reprezint&#259; societatea doar <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span>\nîmpreun&#259;, prin acordul lor unanim, <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nîl pot împuternici pe unul dintre ei s&#259; încheie anumite <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> sau tipuri de <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_827505619\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2127\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_827505619\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Consiliul de supraveghere reprezint&#259; societatea în\nraporturile cu directoratul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1403531538\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2126\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1403531538\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Directoratul înregistreaz&#259; la registrul <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> numele membrilor s&#259;i, <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionând</span> dac&#259; ei <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span>\nîmpreun&#259; sau separat.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}